1- blastpgp -i $DIR_DATA/${id}.fa -d $SNIC_TMP/db/uniref90.fasta -e 0.01 -o $DIR_OUT_ALSN/${id}.alsn.blast -Q $DIR_OUT_PSSM/${id}.pssm -j 4 
or what they use in loctree2
1- blastpgp -F F -a 8 -j 3 -b 3000 -e 1 -h 1e-3 -d /path_to_big80_database/big_80 -i /path/example.fasta -o /path/example.blastPsiOutTmp -C /path/example.chk -Q /path/example.profile
2- loctree2 --fasta /usr/share/doc/loctree2/examples/arch/arch_example.fa --blastmat /usr/share/doc/loctree2/examples/arch/arch_example.profile --resfile ./arch_output.lc2 --domain arch
